naldo in a bid to persuade his unsettled star not to quit the club, Spanish sports daily Marca claimed on Sunday. June 18, 2017 In "News" Real Madrid vs Barcelona: Barcelona coach Luis Enrique revelled in turning the tables on bitter rivals Real Madrid as Lionel Messi struck deep into stoppage time to edge a thrilling El Clasico 3-2 on Sunday. Messi's second goal of the night was his 500th for Barcelona and took the Catalans… April 24, 2017 In "Sports" Argentina captain Lionel Messi has urged his compatriots to be realistic in their World Cup expectations, warning that other teams heading to Russia are better. May 28, 2018 In "Sports"